        boolean validate(AFField field,
                 java.lang.StringBuilder errorMsgs,
                 com.tomscz.afrest.rest.dto.AFValidationRule rule)
        Validates specific validation rule of specific field. Appends error message if validation failed.

        field - field on which should be validation checked
        errorMsgs - string builder to potentially append error message
        rule - specific validation rule which should be checked
